public static final class SocialContract.PeopleActivity
extends Object
implements SocialContract.SyncColumns, SocialContract.BaseSyncColumns, SocialContract.RecommendationColumns

Represents a table containing all the activities that are added to the activity feeds for people. You can search the table using a specific user's global ID as feed owner ID.

Insert

Applications can insert activities. Applications will have to provide the following parameters when inserting activities:
  • GLOBAL_ID (needed temporally until we have a working sync adapter)
  • GLOBAL_ID_FEED_OWNER
  • GLOBAL_ID_ACTOR
  • GLOBAL_ID_OBJECT
  • GLOBAL_ID_VERB
  • GLOBAL_ID_TARGET
  • ACCOUNT_TYPE
